=====================================
           ARC HELP
=====================================


::ARC CREATION BASICS::
-------------------------------------
New Arc: Click "New Arc" for fresh start.
  - Arc Name: Title (max 18 chars).
  - Estimated Type: E2F, E2S, SHT, LHT.
  - Estimated Parts: Numerics by type (e.g., 3:2:3).
  - Zone Type: Safe, Crawl, Fight, Mix0-3, Mixed.
  - Start Msg: Initial lore (max 150 chars).
  - Map: ID/name.
  - Map Type: Import/Generate.
  - Arc Data: Scripts/events (see arc.guide).
  - Confirm Msg: End text (max 150 chars).


::EDITING ARCS::
-------------------------------------
Select Arc: Click list to load.
Modify Fields: Edit; auto-save on blur.
Undo/Redo Arc: Revert/reapply changes.
Delete Arc: Remove (recover via Undo Arc Delete).
Attach to Map: Link to current tab (green dots).
Save Arc: To .arcs file.
Load Arc: From .arcs (overwrite).
Load to Map: Load + attach.
Save Selected: Export current.
Save from Map: Export attached.
Save from Dict: Export all incl. attached.


::SCRIPT GENERATOR::
-------------------------------------
Select Type: Enemy/Boss/Mini-Boss/NPC/Group/Location/Keys.
Fill Fields: Name, rates, color, etc.
Pick Location: Canvas click for XY/object.
Inject: Add formatted string to Arc Data.


::DATA PHRASES::
-------------------------------------
Click buttons: Insert "exit", "kill", etc.


::ARC OPTIONS::
-------------------------------------
Save Arc: Commit to list.
Load Arc: From file.
Undo/Redo: Current edits.
Remove Edits: Clear to defaults.
Clear Data: Arc-Data only.
Clear Fields: All data fields.
Clear Scripts: Script generator only.

